stretch-pwd
===========

This program improve to pretty look for Shell prompt


Contents
========
	* Build and install stretch-pwd
	* Setup for zsh
    * Example


Build and install stretch-pwd
=============================
cd stretch-pwd
make
sudo make install


Setup for zsh
=============
Set fook to a chpwd function in your .zshrc
	
	PS1_WIDTH=30
	function chpwd(){
	    PS1="%B%m%b:`stretch-pwd -l $PS1_WIDTH` %# "
	}

Reload configuration
$ source .zshrc

Example
=======

/usr/local/bin/stretch-pwd -l 25 /home/hashimoto/stretch-pwd
-> /home/hashi...stretch-pwd

/usr/local/bin/stretch-pwd -c ' + ' -l 25 /home/hashimoto/stretch-pwd                                                                                                                                                                           [05/27 16:52:16]
-> /home/hashi + stretch-pwd
